# â— Harmonic Series Calculator

A JavaScript mini application that calculates the **sum of the harmonic series** up to a given number `n`.

## ğŸ“Œ Description
The harmonic series is defined as:

S = 1/1 + 1/2 + 1/3 + ... + 1/n

The user enters a positive integer `n`, and the application calculates the sum using a loop and displays the result.

